ZH: 这个贩子卖的货物都是假的。
EN: The goods sold by this peddler are all fake.

ZH: 我们应该远离贩子，避免购买劣质商品。
EN: We should stay away from peddlers to avoid buying inferior products.

ZH: 这个贩子总是骗人，不能信任他。
EN: This peddler is always deceitful, we can't trust him.

ZH: 警察逮捕了那个贩子，他被判入狱。
EN: The police arrested the peddler and he was sentenced to prison.

ZH: 城市里经常有贩子在街头兜售各种商品。
EN: Peddlers are often selling various goods on the streets in the city.

ZH: 他是一个老实的贩子，从不欺骗顾客。
EN: He is an honest peddler who never deceives customers.

ZH: 那个贩子因为非法售卖商品获得了丰厚的利润。
EN: That peddler gained huge profits from selling goods illegally.

ZH: 这个贩子一直以来都是黑市交易的重要人物。
EN: This peddler has always been an important figure in black market transactions.

ZH: 这个贩子的行为造成了社会的不稳定。
EN: The actions of this peddler have caused social instability.

ZH: 贩子们聚集在市场上，吆喝着自己的商品。
EN: Peddlers gather in the market, shouting about their goods.

ZH: 这家商店因为与贩子合作而被关闭。
EN: This store was closed down due to collaboration with peddlers.

ZH: 警方严厉打击非法贩子的活动。
EN: The police severely crack down on the activities of illegal peddlers.

ZH: 北京街头的贩子们十分热情地招呼着过往行人。
EN: Peddlers on the streets of Beijing warmly greet passersby.

ZH: 贩子们利用黑市赚取了大笔钱财。
EN: Peddlers made a lot of money through the black market.

ZH: 这个贩子常常在邮差来的时候推销商品。
EN: This peddler often promotes goods when the postman comes.

ZH: 警察在巡逻中发现了一个贩卖违禁品的贩子。
EN: The police discovered a peddler selling contraband while patrolling.

ZH: 这名贩子为了生计不得已从事非法活动。
EN: This peddler is forced to engage in illegal activities for a living.

ZH: 贩子们涌入这个城市，危害了当地居民的利益。
EN: Peddlers flooded into this city, harming the interests of local residents.

ZH: 当局已经采取措施整治这些贩子的行为。
EN: Authorities have taken measures to rectify the behavior of these peddlers.
